data.text:
46-DATE TOUR BEGINS SEPTEMBER 19 IN LEXINGTON, KENTUCKY

August 28, 2018 – Hot on the heels of his appearance at the 2018 iHeartRadio MMVAs, Francesco Yates has announced that he will be returning to the road with Justin Timberlake on the third leg of his “Man of the Woods” North American tour. The 46-date tour will see Yates bringing his dynamic show to cities thoughout Canada and the USA. See below for a full list of dates.

When Yates opened the first leg of Canadian dates on this tour in the spring of 2018, the Toronto Star said “Yates served notice with his own animated, choreographing-heavy performance that he intends to enter the same lofty stratosphere occupied by Timberlake, Bruno Mars and Prince if given the chance.”

Earlier this summer, Yates released “Somebody Like You” to follow up on his hit single “Do You Think About Me.” In addition to the new music, Yates also offered fans a peek into his creative process with a video taking fans behind the scenes of the making of “Somebody Like You” which can be seen below.

For all the latest on Yates follow him on Instagram, Twitter, Facebook and YouTube.
